repo = mock(spec=epab.utils.Repo)
CTX.repo = repo
now = datetime.datetime.utcnow()
timestamp = f'{now.year}{now.month}{now.day}{now.hour}{now.minute}'
package_name = config.PACKAGE_NAME()
when(repo).get_current_branch().thenReturn('branch')
when(repo).get_sha().thenReturn('sha')
when(elib_run).run(
    f'dummy.exe ./dist/{package_name}.exe /high version /va /pv version /s desc {package_name} /s product {package_name} /s title {package_name} /s copyright {now.year}-etcher /s company etcher /s SpecialBuild version /s PrivateBuild version-branch_sha-{timestamp} /langid 1033'
    )
when(epab.utils).resource_path(...).thenReturn('dummy.exe')
freeze._patch('version')
